snippet.title: Amber Heard Opens Up About Her Domestic Violence Experience In PSA | NowThis
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Opens Up About Her Domestic Violence Experience In PSA - "When it happens in your home, behind closed doors, with someone you love, it's not as straightforward."
Amber Heard is championing survivor of domestic violence. She opened up about her experience with abuse in a PSA for #GirlGaze Project. She filed for divorce from Johnny Depp in May.
